title: [Commie] Lupin the Third - Mine Fujiko to Iu Onna - 08 [0C305D46
description:
Lupin III Mine Fujiko to Iu Onna - Episode 08



Many people are falling prey to a suspicious new religion. Lupin III infiltrates this group, hoping to steal the treasure their leader keeps hidden. There he lays eyes on the beautiful, bewitching woman who has the leader enthralled. This is the story of how fashionable female thief Fumiko Mine first met Lupin III, the greatest theif of his generation.
